The '''List of mire landscapes in Switzerland''' is a list of Swiss [[bogs]] and [[wetland]]s. It is from the ''Federal Inventory of Mire Landscapes of Particular Beauty and National Importance'' in [[Switzerland]]. <ref>[http://eunis.eea.europa.eu/designations-factsheet.jsp?fromWhere=en&idDesign=CH07&geoscope=34 CDDA: Mire Landscapes of National Importance]</ref>
